description:
Description:-
UIConfig file not found in app/scripts/services/UIConfigService.js, giving "Configuration file not found" in console but UIConfig exists in config folder

Steps to Reproduce:-
Move to http://openmf.github.io/community-app/#/ and check console

Expected Behaviour:-
Should not give that error.

Actual Behaviour:-
Giving error message in console

Settings:-
Mifos X version: 17.07.01.RELEASE
Browser used:chrome
OS:ubuntu
name: UIConfig file not found in app/scripts/services/UIConfigService.js
